Program: Discovery
Title: The Life Scientific: Andrea Sella - Chemist
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ygcn9
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 7 Oct 2012
Andrea Sella is a science showman, whose theatrical demonstrations of chemistry are filling theatres up and down the country. He talks to Jim al-Khalili about his life scientific. Andrea is also Professor of Materials and Inorganic Chemistry at University College London and he and Jim discuss whether he would rather be known for his research into rare metals than for his whizz bang displays. Show less